  <TITLE>Add an option to display only attribute combinations that exist and have stock greater than zero</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>We already have a similar product option implemented (&quot;Allow only existing attribute combinations&quot;). It does not allow to add non-existing combinations to the cart. And this work item is just to display/hide such combination in the public store BEFORE a customer click &quot;add to cart&quot; (client-side validation). Also note that it can cause some issues when you have several attributes. Once choosing one of attributes, it can hide other attributes which actually have some stock with some other value of the first attribute please note that we already support display of stock levels for attribute combinations (dynamic) Also see https://github.com/nopSolutions/nopCommerce/issues/2909 (example of UI implementation)</DESCRIPTION>
